Log for additions to peak-path/python
-------------------------------------

**************************************************************************
05.01.17 (MA)

Added pksc2npz.py which reads in a set of pksc files matching a pattern 
and outputs a .npz file containing either 
 (halo mass, comoving distance;			ipos=0, ivel=0)
 (halo mass, comoving distance, velocity;	ipos=0, ivel=1)
 (halo mass, position;				ipos=1, ivel=0
 (halo mass, position, velocity;		ipos=1, ivel=1)
Usage:
  pksc2npz.py <Mmin [Msun/h]> <zmax> <pattern> <fileout> \
              <write positions [=0]> <write velocities [=0]>

